<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 18:20:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国商务提名人士说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/report-tsmc-chips-made-huawei-huge-concern-us-commerce-nominee-says-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的提名人周四在监督中国的出口政策上，称台湾半导体制造业公司（Saimiciconductor Manufacturing）的报告为华为“大量担忧”生产了成千上万的筹码。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 16:53:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/report-tsmc-chips-made-huawei-huge-concern-us-commerce-nominee-says-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>苹果提起手表的“碳中性”主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-sued-over-carbon-neutral-claim-watches-2025-02-27/</link><description>苹果曾被消费者起诉，他们说其说明三种版本的苹果手表是“碳中性”的，环保友好的是虚假和误导性的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:30:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-sued-over-carbon-neutral-claim-watches-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>COP30总裁说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-plays-key-role-climate-change-may-be-looked-additional-leadership-cop30-2025-02-27/</link><description>COP30主席安德烈·阿兰哈·科雷亚·洛戈（Andre Aranha Correa do Lago Lago）周四表示，中国在应对气候变化方面起着非常重要的作用，其他人可能会寻求亚洲国家的额外领导地位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:23:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-plays-key-role-climate-change-may-be-looked-additional-leadership-cop30-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>巴西食品加工机说2025年食品销售超出了期望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-food-processor-says-2025-food-sales-exceed-expectations-2025-02-27/</link><description>高管周四表示，上市的肉类加工商BRF周四表示，食品销售超出了巴西的头两个月的预期，该公司计划扩大加工食品的生产，以从强劲的需求中获取收入。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-food-processor-says-2025-food-sales-exceed-expectations-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>洛根集团（Logan Group）从80％</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/logan-group-secures-backing-over-80-creditors-8-billion-debt-revamp-2025-02-27/</link><description>总部位于深圳的房地产开发商洛根集团（Logan Group）周四表示，已获得80.8％以上债权人的重组提案的支持，他们共同持有62.1亿美元的未偿还离岸债务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 15:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/logan-group-secures-backing-over-80-creditors-8-billion-debt-revamp-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普誓言3月4日对加拿大墨西哥的关税，中国超过芬太尼的10％</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/trump-says-mexico-canada-tariffs-take-effect-march-4-2025-02-27/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周四表示，他提议对墨西哥和加拿大商品的25％关税将于3月4日生效，并威胁要对中国进口商品承担10％的责任，因为致命毒品仍在从这些国家涌入美国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 13:56:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/trump-says-mexico-canada-tariffs-take-effect-march-4-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国小米价格豪华电轿车比最初促进的低35％</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-prices-luxury-electric-sedan-72932-2025-02-27/</link><description>中国的小米周四将其豪华电动轿车SU7 Ultra的初始标价降低了三分之一至529,900元（72,931.72美元），对世界上最大的汽车市场的特斯拉和波斯奇等人带来了更大的挑战。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 13:14:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-prices-luxury-electric-sedan-72932-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在4月1日之后决定所有国家的关税政策，哈塞特告诉CNBC</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-decide-tariff-policies-after-april-1-hassett-tells-cnbc-2025-02-27/</link><description>白宫经济顾问凯文·哈塞特（Kevin Hassett）在周四的一次采访中告诉CNBC，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）将在4月1日进行研究后，将对包括墨西哥和加拿大在内的所有国家做出关税政策。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 13:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-decide-tariff-policies-after-april-1-hassett-tells-cnbc-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着贸易战的升级，经济学家押注中国的韧性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/trade-war-escalates-economists-bet-china-resilience-2025-02-27/</link><description>随着中国处于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税议程的最前沿，国内经济学家预计，随着贸易战的加剧，政策措施，供应链调整和加强全球合作伙伴关系的结合，加强了全球第二大经济体。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 12:19:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/trade-war-escalates-economists-bet-china-resilience-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>小米推出了15个超旗舰智能手机，价格为894美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-launches-15-ultra-flagship-smartphone-priced-894-2025-02-27/</link><description>世界第三大智能手机制造商小米（小米）在周四推出了新的旗舰智能手机小米15 Ultra，基本型号的起价为6,499元（894.19美元）。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 12:06:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-launches-15-ultra-flagship-smartphone-priced-894-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>医疗保健专家敦促印度重写临床试验规则，以提高全球市场份额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/healthcare-experts-urge-india-rewrite-clinical-trial-rules-boost-global-market-2025-02-27/</link><description>医疗保健专家在一次行业会议上说，印度应该从中国和澳大利亚等国家的剧本中获取一页。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 11:43:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/healthcare-experts-urge-india-rewrite-clinical-trial-rules-boost-global-market-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>早上出价：即使是Nvidia Beat也会耸耸肩，关税战争迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-02-27/</link><description>看看美国和迈克·多兰（Mike Dolan）的全球市场的前一天</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 11:05:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>法国工业部长说，欧盟钢铁行业需要更多的保护</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/europes-steel-industry-needs-greater-protection-says-french-industry-minister-2025-02-27/</link><description>法国行业部长马克·费拉奇（Marc Ferracci）周四表示，由于目前的措施不足，欧洲生病的钢铁部门需要更好地保护廉价进口。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 10:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/europes-steel-industry-needs-greater-protection-says-french-industry-minister-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>腾讯发布了新的AI模型，比DeepSeek-R1更快地回答</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tencent-releases-new-ai-model-says-replies-faster-than-deepseek-r1-2025-02-27/</link><description>中国科技巨头腾讯周四发布了一种新的AI模型，该模型可以比全球DeepSeek的R1更快地回答查询，在最新迹象中，这家初创企业的国内和海外成功是给中国更大的竞争对手施加压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 10:29:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tencent-releases-new-ai-model-says-replies-faster-than-deepseek-r1-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>微软敦促特朗普大修拜登的最后一次AI-CHIP出口路缘</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-will-urge-trump-overhaul-curbs-ai-chip-exports-wsj-reports-2025-02-27/</link><description>微软已敦促唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的团队在竞技政府的结束日内简化对人工智能筹码的出口限制，称这些措施不应扩展到美国盟友。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 10:24:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-will-urge-trump-overhaul-curbs-ai-chip-exports-wsj-reports-2025-02-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>